title: About Sarah
text:
Sarah’s Photo




Hi, I’m Sarah, the founder of Jazz Medical Aesthetics. As a Physician Assistant with a diverse medical background, I’m passionate about helping my clients achieve their aesthetic goals.



 Originally from Buffalo, NY, now based in Stafford, VA
 Undergraduate degree in Business Administration from the University at Buffalo
 PA degree from Daemen University





 8 years in primary care
 Traveling PA providing customized patient care
 Emergency Medicine PA
 Now specializing in medical aesthetics




I created Jazz Medical Aesthetics to offer a unique, personalized approach to aesthetic treatments. By bringing these services directly to you, we ensure a comfortable, convenient experience tailored to your individual needs.
 Book an Appointment

title: Our Services
text:
At Jazz Medical Aesthetics, we bring beauty to you. Our neurotoxin services are offered in the comfort of your home or office for ultimate convenience.



 Jeuveau: The latest FDA-approved neurotoxin for frown lines
 Botox: The classic choice for wrinkle reduction
